title: Racial Relations
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: racial_timer <= 0
max-visits: 100
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; racial_timer += 6;
card-image: img/racial_relations.jpg

= Racial Relations

WIP CARD, A ETHNIC COUNTERPART TO Media

Sri Lanka is a racially diverse nation, and arguably since even our formation in the 50s, ethnic identity and intrests have played a large role in politics. That still hasnt changed.

- @toughertamilline
- @muslimsecurity
- @commercial
- @campaign
- @ideological
- @radio
- @radio_2
- @radio_3
- @television
- @television_2
- @television_3
- @posters
- @post_cards
