- @return: We should not do anything with media at the moment.
- @easy_discard
- @cancel_advisor_action


@toughertamilline
title: The militant and terrorist elements among Tamils are severe threat to Sri Lankan stability. We should argue for tougher action against them.
subtitle: -3 resources
choose-if: resources >= 3
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources. 
on-arrival: resources -= 3; sinhala_slfp += 4; sltamil_slfp -= 2; muslim_slfp += 2.5; sinhala_nationalism += 2.25; tamil_nationalism += 3;

Sinhalese and Muslims take the message well, Tamils however are antagonised by the messaging.

@muslimsecurity
title: Muslims particularily in the North-East have been in the crossfire between militants and police, the SLFP should campaign for greater security for Muslim communities.
subtitle: -3 resources
choose-if: resources >= 3
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources. 
on-arrival: resources -= 3; muslim_slfp += 3.7; 
{!
if (Q.unp_in_government = 1){Q.muslim_unp -= 3}
!}

Muslims appreciate our concern for their often ignored communities. [? if unp_in_government = 1 : This has also siphoned a few of them away from the incumbent UNP who they see as neglecting their concerns. ?]

@theatre
title: In rural areas of Sri Lanka, theatre, plays and musicals are an important part of community and a form of entertainment, perhaps we can organise our own events?
subtitle: -4 resources
choose-if: resources >= 4
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources. 
view-if: theatre = 0
on-arrival: theatre += 1; resources -= 4; rural_slfp += 3; workers_slfp += 1.5;

The songs, acting and general performance gather modest crowds, but they seem enthusiastic at the entertainment provided.

//will be effective on the rural class,

@post_cards
title: A rather novel idea has been brought to our attention. Post cards, fantasy money, flags and other "collectables" presenting party leaders and symbols.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 2
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources. 
view-if: post_cards = 0
on-arrival: post_cards += 1; resources -= 2; middle_slfp += 2.5;

While many question the efficacy of this strategy in spreading our message, loyal party followers are collecting in droves and our coming to rallies clad in blue, waving the party standard.

//will be effective on middle class

@posters
title: Our posters, leaflets and flyers are outdated and need refinment for a changing electorate and their demands.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 2
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources. 
view-if: poster = 0
on-arrival: poster += 2; resources -= 1; middle_slfp += 1.5; workers_slfp +=1.5; rural_slfp += 1.5; upper_slfp += 1.5;

Our party members have unveiled a new "series" of posters with chatchy slogans and innovative art styles. This will surely make our party more presentable.

//will be broadly effective

@television
title: With greater TV ownership among Sri Lankans, moving into the medium can be benefical in spreading our message directly in the form of ads or programs.
subtitle: -3 resources
choose-if: resources >= 3 and private_tv = 1
unavailable-subtitle: The government maintains a monopoly on television. Not enough resources. 
view-if: tv_ad = 0
on-arrival: tv_ad += 1; resources -= 3; middle_slfp += 2; workers_slfp += 2.5; rural_slfp += 0.75; upper_slfp += 2.5;

Our adoption of the TV for political messaging is rather unprecedented in Sri Lanka and already other parties are starting to adopt the medium as well, time will tell if it will be effective.

//will be more effective for working class people and middle class people

@television_2
title: To keep up with the quality of private and public TV, we need to continue funding our operations.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
view-if: tv_ad > 0 and tv_ad <= 4
on-arrival: radio += 1; resources -= 2; middle_slfp += 2.25; workers_slfp += 2.75; rural_slfp += 1.25; upper_slfp += 1.25; 

Our ads, and programs are reaching nearlly everycorner of the country, our message is spreading far and wide.

@television_3
title: We should keep on supporting our TV operations.
subtitle: Our operations are now running smoothly, if we regularily fund it we can continue to maintain and improve it. -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
view-if: tv_ad > 4 
on-arrival: tv_ad += 1; resources -= 1; middle_slfp += 3; workers_slfp += 3.5; rural_slfp += 1.5; upper_slfp += 2; 

We are continuing to invest in our TV operations.

@commercial
title: Make our newspapers more commercialized by broadening their appeal beyond party supporters.
subtitle: This might upset ideological purists, but it may bring in more funds and perhaps expose the middle class to socialist views.
on-arrival: resources += 1; left_dissent += 10; nationalist_strength += 3;

Our commercialized newspapers are able to bring in more funds. However, the Left express's their displeasure. The Nationalists are by contrast are mildly enthusiastic.

@campaign
title: The purpose of our media is to rally support for the SLFP.
subtitle: Our newspapers will focus on the electoral campaign.
on-arrival: campaign_media += 1; middle_slfp += 0.75; workers_slfp += 0.75; rural_slfp += 0.75; upper_slfp += 0.75;

Our campaign media makes the rounds but with it being such a broad sweep, the campaign is not as effective esspecially with how saturated the landscape has become.

@ideological
title: We will have vibrant ideological debate within our newspapers.
subtitle: There will be space for the two sides to air their views.
on-arrival: left_dissent -= 4; nationalist_dissent -= 4; middle_slfp -= 0.5; workers_slfp -= 0.5; rural_slfp -= 0.5; upper_slfp -= 0.5;

With our internal feuding bleeding into our publications, the mood internally is somewhat improved, the public however are concerned about the lack of direction and instability.

@radio
title: Why not fund a radio station?
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 2 and private_radio = 1
unavailable-subtitle: The government maintains a monopoly on radio. Not enough resources. 
view-if: radio = 0
on-arrival: radio += 1; resources -= 2; middle_slfp += 0.75; workers_slfp += 0.75; rural_slfp += 0.75; upper_slfp += 0.75;

Our new radio station allows us to connect to people in a more intimate setting than before, spreading our message along with music and other popular content. 

@radio_2
title: We must keep on building up our radio network.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
view-if: radio > 0 and radio <= 4
on-arrival: radio += 1; resources -= 2; middle_slfp += 1.25; workers_slfp += 1.30; rural_slfp += 2.25; upper_slfp += 1.25; 

Our new radio network has a mix of popular and political programming, and is proving a success.

@radio_3
title: We should keep on supporting our radio network.
subtitle: The station is now running smoothly, if we regularily fund it we can continue to maintain and improve it. -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
view-if: radio > 4 
on-arrival: radio += 1; resources -= 1; middle_slfp += 2; workers_slfp += 2.25; rural_slfp += 3.5; upper_slfp += 2; 

We are continuing to invest in our radio station. 